Qatar has a major rivalry against [[Bahrain national football team|Bahrain]] due to historical tension between the two countries. With 39 matches played, the overall record favours Bahrain, who won 11 matches, lost 8, and tied 19. From 2004 until 2021, Qatar suffered a winless streak over Bahrain with six defeats and ten draws before finally registering a win in the [[2021 FIFA Arab Cup]].

